==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nuclear weapon
<hw>Nu"cle*ar wea"pon</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A weapon of
great explosive power, such as an <stype>atomic bomb</stype> or a
<stype>hydrogen bomb</stype>, which depends for most of its explosive
power on the release of energy from within atomic nuclei by a nuclear
reaction. A <stype>fission weapon</stype> or a <stype>fusion
weapon</stype>. The term includes atomic shells for cannon.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>nuclear winter</ent>⟦br⟧
